        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 18 at 6:54PM CDT by NWS Houston/Galveston TX</headline>
        <description>At 654 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a cluster of strong
thunderstorms over Jersey Village, moving north at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Sugar Land, Stafford, Katy, Richmond, Tomball, Jersey Village,
Brookshire, Bunker Hill Village, Town West, Pecan Grove, Spring
Branch North, Eldridge / West Oaks, Spring Branch West, Addicks Park
Ten, Mission Bend, Spring Valley, Greater Greenspoint, Meadows Place,
Hedwig Village, and Fulshear.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
